section_2_text.eng:
Involves processing foods during periods of abundance/when there is plenty of rainfall and high biomass production, to be used during periods of scarcity. We should preserve;
 * Food for people- solar drying and preservation of vegetables and fruits
 * Feeds for livestock- Fermented feeds, hay, and silage making

